{
  "stem": "26576.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because we saw-- it's interesting what I saw on television now, the story was Chechens.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I suddenly remember it must have been 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "A few thousand Chechens were brought to Merke in exactly the same trains that we were going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they were left to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "After a few months, there was not a single Chechen left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They got-- either they were shot or they died from that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they disappeared, and we were asking what happened to the Chechens, among ourselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they all said, oh, they were cooperating with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So at that stage, I was thinking that all the Chechens cooperated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Later on we heard different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But at this time, so we didn't go into any politics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were happy to be alive, and happy so to struggle, and to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Also as I said before, it's very-- it was very close to the Chinese border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had bandits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was a no man's land.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You know, there were very tall mountains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we were-- Merke was very close to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So sometimes in the morning we would see one of the people from [NON-ENGLISH] there would be killed by the bandits.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was a lot of bandits living in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Those were sort of like people that ran away from the Russian regime, or all kinds of people that were unhappy with what was happening in Russia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And so we were scared of the bandits also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Like we wouldn't venture out further.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Anyway, so among-- even now I have photographs of the children in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I had quite a happy time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Mind you, the conditions in which we were going to school were terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But you couldn't compare them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
